summary: Five gates.   For ages they stood sealed. Buried deep in the catacombs of an ancient castle. Long-forgotten.  But now they stand open.  It is said that the First brings the cold, and the Second leads the darkness with it.  The Third, fear, the Fourth, pain.   And the Fifth Gate… from the Fifth Gate comes death itself...
descriptionHtml:
[img]http://static2.nexusmods.com/15/mods/110/images/24351-1-1348079587.jpg[/img]

[size=7] [color=Red]Requires Dawnguard![/size] [/color]

Five gates. For ages they stood sealed… buried deep in the catacombs of an ancient castle. Long-forgotten. But now they stand open. It is said that the First brings the cold, and the Second leads the darkness with it. The Third, fear, the Fourth, pain. And the Fifth Gate… from the Fifth Gate comes death itself...

Travel to High Hrothgar and walk down the Throat of the World, until you find the Tomb of the Unknown...

German Version: http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/24767/
